What is AZ copy used for?
Copy blobs or files (only) to or from a storage account

what is azure blob storage used for
Blob (Binary Large Object) Storage is used for storing large amounts of unstructured data like text or binary data

When should I use BLOB storage?
1. serve images or documents to a browser
2. stream audio or video
3. storre fies for  distributed access
4. Store data for backup, DR, and archiving.
5. Store data for analysis by an on-premises or Azure-hosted service.
